ght:108%; margin:0pt 0pt 8pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">These programm</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">es would be better in my view funded by general taxation </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">with </span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">all other television funded by optional subscription which was not on option prior to digital television.</span></p><p style="font-size:11pt; line-height:108%; margin:0pt 0pt 8pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">My motivation for writing in.</span></p><p style="font-size:11pt; line-height:108%; margin:0pt 0pt 8pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">I live in Switzerland with my wife, we pay the Swiss TV li</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">cence and also subscribe to a Pay TV package which includes UK TV channels.</span></p><p style="font-size:11pt; line-height:108%; margin:0pt 0pt 8pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">As our parents are in their late 70’s we keep a small flat near them in order to be able one of us to fly over and look after them at short notice if required. Typically we current</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">ly only live in it a few days a year. </span></p><p style="font-size:11pt; line-height:108%; margin:0pt 0pt 8pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">As we have a TV in the house I have to buy a UK TV Licence even to watch a few days TV which seems absurdly unfair when I am already paying for it over here. </span></p><p style="font-size:11pt; line-height:108%; margin:0pt 0pt 8pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">A further point is that via the internet or cable I can ac</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">cess hundreds of TV channels wherever I am in the world via my Swiss provider &amp; the internet legally- unless I do so in the UK?</span></p><p style="font-size:11pt; line-height:108%; margin:0pt 0pt 8pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">I feel that the BBC has grown into a monster we don’t need to afford any more and we would probably be more creative as a nation</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt"> without it.</span><a name="_GoBack"></a></p><p style="font-size:11pt; line-height:108%; margin:0pt 0pt 8pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="font-size:11pt; line-height:108%; margin:0pt 0pt 8pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt; font-style:italic">October 2013</span></p><p style="font-size:11pt; line-height:108%; margin:0pt 0pt 8pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="font-size:11pt; line-height:108%; margin:0pt 0pt 8pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="font-size:11pt; line-height:108%; margin:0pt 0pt 8pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="font-size:11pt; line-height:108%; margin:0pt 0pt 8pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="font-size:11pt; line-height:108%; margin:0pt 0pt 8pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="font-size:11pt; line-height:108%; margin:0pt 0pt 8pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="font-size:11pt; line-height:108%; margin:0pt 0pt 8pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="font-size:11pt; line-height:108%; margin:0pt 0pt 8pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="font-size:11pt; line-height:108%; margin:0pt 0pt 8pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="font-size:11pt; line-height:108%; margin:0pt 0pt 8pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="font-size:11pt; line-height:108%; margin:0pt 0pt 8pt"><span style="font-family:Cali